can u make so this script switches to ur totem if u go into ur inventory (My totem bind is 3)

"def module legit-totem
def desc "Custom Scripted Module"

on tick if hovering_over #totem !if off_holding #totem if input_active inventory {
    input key z
}

on tick if hovering_over #totem !if hotbar_has #totem if input_active inventory {
    input key 3
}"